<!DOCTYPE translationbundle>
<translationbundle lang="zu">
<translation id="7649299977121480655">Izihloko zesikhangiso zingenye yezinto eziningi isayithi elingazisebenzisa ukuqondanisa izikhangiso nomuntu siqu. Ngisho nangaphandle kwezihloko zezikhangiso, amasayithi asengakubonisa izikhangiso kodwa angase avuse intshisekelo encane. Funda kabanzi mayelana <ph name="BEGIN_LINK_1" />nokuphatha ubumfihlo bezikhangiso zakho<ph name="END_LINK_1" />.</translation>
</translationbundle>